Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯王國？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是這個大陸的中心 很熱鬧對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿利亞差多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…克勞德 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 現在不是做這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此唐突地前來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能得到您的接見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是由衷的感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷吉斯還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是那麼頑固嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你叫克勞德是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想調查索沙隕石是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙隕石所在的艾爾大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受其影響所產生的魔物們\N目前還處於和人們交戰的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有戰況傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過勝利的話應該就會有所傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國派出的特使至今也還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可能會是一趟賭上性命的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你也還是要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你們一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可不要後悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行證你們拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是到艾爾大陸的通行證啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往來大陸之間居然需要通行證
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能就拿不到這張通行證呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是你的功勞喲 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事沒什麼好謝的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的好緊張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然國王的那種威嚴好莊嚴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我識相點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看該識相點的人應該是你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太纏人的男人可不受歡迎喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為你是女人我們才來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是聽說你要找保鏢才來找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我不是拒絕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事哪是你說了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總要把理由說清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得太醜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們三個並不是我喜歡的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你們還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為是女人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三大男人欺負一個女人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟 想打架嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有沒有聽見啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定選你當我的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…我們的話可還沒說完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用你的髒手碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢碰我的身體 就得有相當的覺悟的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要做個了斷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 很危險喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退後一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我們怎麼修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沈睡於吾體內的紅蓮之火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉火界王派蒙之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此解放汝等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聖三角的引導下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將阻擋在吾面前者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予灼熱的制裁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰之矢！(Fire Bolt)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塞麗奴·茱莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我叫做克勞德……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德 那我們走吧… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經是我的保鏢了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯洞窟馬上就要到了喲 克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德在搞什麼嘛 還會不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來和我們的目的地完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯的秘寶到底是什麼樣的寶藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏好興奮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏獵人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是一流的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的招術呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不知道 紋章術 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紋章術？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用刻畫在身上某種特定形狀的紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將念力轉換成各種不同形態的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分為空氣 水 火 地 等圖形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將天魔之名作為烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能作為 紋章術 使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我來說 像我剛才使用火系法術的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是利用掌管 火 的三角形的紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角形的紋章…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 浮現在這裏喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…我好像沒有要你一起跟過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼需要克勞德呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過讓他做我的保鏢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用那種紋章術的紋章術師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不需要什麼保鏢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧 克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的又不是寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是索沙隕石才對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙隕石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是我聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說克洛斯洞窟由於索沙隕石的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像受到影響什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到索沙隕石的影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 塞麗奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的 我沒聽過這樣的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只能怪你的消息不夠靈通咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到鎮上問問看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在就去確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本就沒這回事喲^^
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的到了那裡就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有白跑一趟的心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比沒去 事後後悔要來的好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然克勞德你都這麼說了……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就往克洛斯洞窟前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的還要大耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是濕濕的…感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這麼快就有岔路了啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走哪一邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看地圖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼黑看不到耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我去弄點火照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混濁之泉沐浴的明界王拉格甦醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是紋章術師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 ……這張是藏寶圖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒禮貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我在克洛斯王國最大的拍賣會上\N好不容易競標得來的真品喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還附有鑑定書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏寶圖居然會有鑑定書 這不是很可疑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 走左邊這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了現在的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太沒用了吧 只不過是蝙蝠而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是人家第一次看到蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說塞麗奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西受到了索沙隕石的影響嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…真的有…真的有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果還不能走路就再休息一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  年輕就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過麻煩你們走快一點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？這還真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒路了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第七次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直照著地圖走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖上畫的還有路可走的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地圖果然是假貨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回頭吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹她生氣了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀……討厭蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭蟲子啦 討厭討厭……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 塞麗奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她要僱傭保鏢的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 塞麗奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把蟲子丟掉了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這個人還真可愛…呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…人家嚇的心跳的好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞利奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西…過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲…蟲…蟲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一條！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這是什麼跟什麼啊 真是受不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人還真誠實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過肚子還真是餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些餅乾如果可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有一點受潮 但是這個時候就湊合著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐 這些餅乾是為了克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的你們兩個就分著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一塊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我肚子還不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？　克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀　還挺親熱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞…塞麗奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人羨慕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當個一流的寶藏獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有談戀愛的空閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在炫耀？還是在埋怨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張地圖一定是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道我花了多少錢才買到它的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的胸部會被磨小的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是什麼啊　真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦　這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是歪打正著　運氣真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是舊文明的遺址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們好像被塞麗奴小姐給唬弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡根本沒有什麼跟索沙隕石有關的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　果然塞麗奴她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？話說回來塞麗奴小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊　你們倆快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯的秘寶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏發現了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡裝了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你不是沒感興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼石像…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是索沙隕石的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些石像上附著守護靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前曾經聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊文明時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮廷的紋章術師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便讓靈魂附著在武器或者是石像上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 居然彈開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它根本就毫髮無傷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能打倒它們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一會兒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能幫我暫時纏住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試試一個紋章術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個咒文的詠唱很長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在咒文詠唱的途中被他們打斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文就無法完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物們　寶藏在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤聖三角的引導下 控制火的火界王派蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀新月的引導下 控制水的水界王亞裏頓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金正方的引導下 控制地的地界王阿邁蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青圓的引導下　控制月的空氣界王奧裏姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在支配自然界的汝等之佑護下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導這藍錐圓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭示天地四方 古往今來的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱吾等的四方境界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌管萬物的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完嗎　塞麗奴？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞利奴　快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以照耀四方的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予吾等白朮之光吧！
